list.name: Changes
list.comment:
refactor: restructure modules and remove unused code
- Removed unused codecs, models, and traits (e.g., `BytesCodec`, `Hasher`, `KafkaTransportEnvelope`). - Consolidated domain value packages under `algebra.value` for clarity. - Added `processor-lambda` module and updated `build.sbt` with dependencies. - Adjusted `NodeAddress` logic and refined compilation steps. - Cleaned up infrastructure for improved maintainability.
